"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:31:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇野可以證明你入過?</blockquote><br />\n有</blockquote><br />\npost出黎睇睇</blockquote><br />\n佢地識我知我住邊 怕比人起底不了</blockquote><br />\n此post已完<br />\n<br />\n大家可以唔使理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得鳩UP, 佢話自己係共產黨都得</blockquote><br />\n我唔係共產黨"},{"pid":"51ffe64e155a6cbc9c3596019dc3695fa6f9581c","tid":357852,"uid":47027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:35:31.000Z","msg":"你嗰時屌人定俾人屌on9?"},{"pid":"ad90638c1904e7fb0808204309e3041215feace1","tid":357852,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T16:31:34.000Z","msg":"咁似之前我個acc出果個膠Post既"},{"pid":"9ce7164d73086f05a401a673b197fa7d36f93693","tid":357852,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T19:15:31.000Z","msg":"關人撚事咩，繼續打飛機啦你"},{"pid":"94412dc4be14fdadfaa8c7b5dede0bf27fb6dd1b","tid":357852,"uid":13825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T19:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不如你自己講啦"},{"pid":"cf43e04eb6c177d066500efd608c85b1522eb536","tid":357852,"uid":65649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T19:54:46.000Z","msg":"條撚樣d post來來去去都係反包皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假膠居多，勿信"},{"pid":"79cd7c969d8c091fd42e395e1fddf881d680ff4f","tid":357852,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T19:55:58.000Z","msg":"1.)當初點解要加入？<br />\n2.)最後點解要退出？<br />\n3.)可唔可以分享一件令你感受最深既事？<br />\n4.)依段經歷令你有咩得著？<br />\n<br />\n5.)覺得你退出個陣既熱血公民，同係最初加入個陣有冇唔同？如果有，有咩唔同？<br />\n6.)你仲係熱狗既時候，你覺得外界係點睇你？"},{"pid":"c7c9d92b0c344f3359b0388542a554bb341b2b3a","tid":357852,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T19:56:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條撚樣d post來來去去都係反包皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假膠居多，勿信</blockquote><br />\n熱狗質素係咁上下"},{"pid":"595fea1535411f6e38cd766903f888702142ea24","tid":357852,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T20:01:49.000Z","msg":"7.) 當時身為熱狗既你，同目前既你；對於以下幾個組織/人物既評價有冇唔同？如果有，講下分別係邊，點解唔同。<br />\n<br />\n陳雲/城邦派<br />\n<br />\n民族黨<br />\n<br />\n青政<br />\n<br />\n習近平"},{"pid":"2c1fd01c2f1f37670af1815fe4fac9addaed0fc9","tid":357852,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T20:09:15.000Z","msg":"8.)你認為熱血公民未來既發展會係點？興盛還是衰落？政治/經營路線會唔會改變？人事會唔會再有變用？<br />\n<br />\n9.)你認為過去熱血公民對本土主義運動有咩影響？<br />\n<br />\n10.)點睇香港公民社會往後既發展？<br />\n<br />\n11.)有咩想同目前同未來既熱狗講？"},{"pid":"5be1a1d10cb010f4e6f635a0cf0f0bba775a5163","tid":357852,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:14:24.000Z","msg":"有冇同殘獸胃扑過嘢？"},{"pid":"c3f354f954ba7a1f4ef227d1be2da769a45e0fad","tid":357852,"uid":31521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:19:43.000Z","msg":"你入過邊個熱血公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n陳雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7138449a93d1281b2500e6f932d31d9640a5a66e","tid":357852,"uid":136317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇同殘獸胃扑過嘢？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}